    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>zingy dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and add<strong> </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>zingy dressing </strong>and toss – this is your <strong>zingy salad</strong></p>",
